Package ca.uqac.lif.cep.io

Processors to handle input and output of data from external sources, such as files and pipes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Caller
    Processor calling an external command upon receiving an event, and returning the output of that command as its output stream.
    FileWriter
    Writes events to a file on disk
    HttpReader
    Reads chunks of data from an URL, using an HTTP request.
    IoPalette  
    LineReader
    Special case of stream reader reading lines from an input stream.
    LineTokenFeeder  
    PackageExtension  
    StreamReader
    Reads chunks of data from an input source.
